## NavItem Interface

```typescript
interface NavItem {
  icon: string;              // Emoji icon (20px display size)
  label: string;             // Display name
  path: string;              // Route path
  shortcut?: string;         // Optional keyboard shortcut letter
  hasSettings?: boolean;     // Show settings gear button (hover)
  children?: NavItem[];      // Sub-pages (makes item expandable)
  defaultExpanded?: boolean; // Initial expansion state
}
```

