## Visual Specifications

### Spacing & Sizing
- **Item Height:** `h-10` (40px) for parent items
- **Child Height:** `h-9` (36px) for sub-items
- **Icon Size:** `w-5 h-5` (20px) for main icons
- **Child Icon Size:** `w-4 h-4` (16px) for child icons
- **Button Size:** `w-5 h-5` (20px) for expand/collapse buttons
- **Gap:** `gap-3` (12px) between elements
- **Padding:** `px-3` (12px horizontal padding)
- **Child Indentation:** `ml-6` (24px left margin)

### Button Alignment (Critical!)
All buttons within a navigation item must be aligned horizontally:
1. Icon (left, 20px)
2. Label (flex-1, takes remaining space)
3. Settings button (if `hasSettings: true`, 20px)
4. Expand/collapse button (if has children, 20px)

**Layout Pattern:**
```
[Icon] [Label................] [⚙️] [▶]
  20px  flex-1                20px  20px
```

### Drag Behavior
- **Entire Item Draggable:** The whole `<li>` element has drag listeners
- **Cursor:** `cursor-grab` on hover, `cursor-grabbing` when dragging
- **No Separate Handle:** No drag handle icon (removed as of 2025-11-27)
- **Activation Distance:** 5px movement required to start drag
- **Visual Feedback:** `opacity: 0.5` while dragging

