## Keyboard & Accessibility

### Keyboard Shortcuts
- **Cmd/Ctrl + B:** Toggle sidebar collapse
- **Cmd/Ctrl + D:** Open today's daily note (if enabled)

### ARIA Attributes
- Sidebar: `aria-label="Main navigation sidebar"`
- Navigation: `aria-label="Primary navigation"`
- Expand button: `title="Expand" or "Collapse"`
- Settings button: `aria-label="{label} page settings"`

### Focus Management
- All buttons must be keyboard accessible
- Focus states must be visible (`:focus-visible`)
- Tab order must be logical

