## Common Pitfalls

### ❌ Wrong: Hardcoded Colors
```tsx
<div className="bg-blue-500 text-white">
```

### ✅ Right: Semantic Tokens
```tsx
<div className="bg-surface-light-elevated dark:bg-surface-dark-elevated text-text-light-primary dark:text-text-dark-primary">
```

### ❌ Wrong: Inconsistent Button Sizes
```tsx
<button className="w-6 h-6"> {/* 24px - wrong! */}
```

### ✅ Right: Standard Button Size
```tsx
<button className="w-5 h-5"> {/* 20px - correct */}
```

### ❌ Wrong: Missing Expand Button Alignment
```tsx
{/* Settings and expand buttons in separate containers */}
<div>{settingsButton}</div>
<div>{expandButton}</div>
```

### ✅ Right: Buttons in Same Flex Container
```tsx
{/* Both buttons in same parent, using flex gap */}
<>
  {settingsButton}
  {expandButton}
</>
```

